    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254620/extras/cdcf688c47d6b5f58a080965836018cb.avif?t=1740428114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254620/extras_big/cdcf688c47d6b5f58a080965836018cb.avif?t=1740428114 width=800 height=533 /></span>Old Magic Grandtower is a 2 player coop puzzle adventure game, combining tactical floor-breaking combat against fairy-tale creatures with challenging puzzles on every floor. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Floor-breaking combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight on a crumbling tower floor where every skill matters - break, push, pull, and outmaneuver your enemies to send them plunging into the void below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254620/extras/f325605d046e776fc604e8765eba7f8a.avif?t=1740428114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254620/extras_big/f325605d046e776fc604e8765eba7f8a.avif?t=1740428114 width=800 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Navigate intricate puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve challenging puzzles that require clever teamwork - combine both heroes' unique abilities to overcome obstacles and ascend the Tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254620/extras/52756915a27539e14863d1a1e65d295b.avif?t=1740428114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254620/extras_big/52756915a27539e14863d1a1e65d295b.avif?t=1740428114 width=800 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Stained Spire</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your main goal is to reach the top of the Old Tower, uncovering the dark secrets within and discovering the origins of the Ink Apocalypse that shattered the fairy-tale world 30 years ago.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlikely Allies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of Red Riding Hood and the Big Bad Wolf, both forever changed by the years following the Ink Apocalypse. Red, a war-hardened veteran struggling with PTSD, joins forces with the Wolf, who's grown weary of his villainous reputation and seeks to forge his own path through humanity.</p>",
